[SPEAKER_00] istraživanju tajna ljudske sreće.

347
00:16:41,679 --> 00:16:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta su otkrili?

348
00:16:42,639 --> 00:16:46,139
[SPEAKER_00] Da nije sreća ugoda plus uspjeh,

349
00:16:46,139 --> 00:16:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] nego istina plus ljubav.

350
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] U zdravim, dobrim, sebedarnim,

351
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:54,259
[SPEAKER_00] nesebičnim, čistim odnosima.

352
00:16:54,259 --> 00:16:57,919
[SPEAKER_00] Kad čovjek počme prijateljeva s Bogom,

353
00:16:57,919 --> 00:16:59,080
[SPEAKER_00] kao s osobom,

354
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne da obavi nekakvu molitvu radi reda,

355
00:17:01,460 --> 00:17:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] što se nama svima može dogoditi,

356
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] makar je bolje tako nego nikako.

357
00:17:04,559 --> 00:17:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] Nego, Bože, mene više niko ne treba tjerat

358
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] da ja želim Tvoju volju.

359
00:17:09,019 --> 00:17:11,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nego upravo zato što volim sebe

360
00:17:11,299 --> 00:17:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] i on je oko sebe.

361
00:17:12,099 --> 00:17:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja te trebam.

362
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad upoznate Božju nesebičnu ljubav,

363
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:18,339
[SPEAKER_00] dogodi se svet i zaborav na sebe.

364
00:17:18,339 --> 00:17:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] Briga mene za mene kad on misli na mene.

365
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ne trebamo biti zabrinuti

366
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo već zbrinuti od njega.

367
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] Imate prekrasnu meditaciju,

368
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:28,200
[SPEAKER_00] svima im preporučam,

369
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse misli ti.

370
00:17:30,039 --> 00:17:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Odolinda, sluge Božjega,

371
00:17:32,559 --> 00:17:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji ga jako cijenio,

372
00:17:33,539 --> 00:17:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] veliki svetac, padre Pio.

373
00:17:34,980 --> 00:17:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nećete najat sveca,

374
00:17:37,119 --> 00:17:39,240
[SPEAKER_00] koji je postao upravo to svet,

375
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] bez otkrivanja

376
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ostvarivanja

377
00:17:42,599 --> 00:17:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Božje volje,

378
00:17:43,539 --> 00:17:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] jedino spasanostne najbolje.

379
00:17:45,319 --> 00:17:46,740
[SPEAKER_00] Nema takvoga.

380
00:17:46,740 --> 00:17:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna od najvećih planetarnih svetnica

381
00:17:49,119 --> 00:17:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] našeg vremena,

382
00:17:49,859 --> 00:17:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] sveta majka Terezija,

383
00:17:51,079 --> 00:17:52,680
[SPEAKER_00] je znana govorit

384
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] da zanosit se ičim drugim

385
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:56,700
[SPEAKER_00] osim voljom Božjom

386
00:17:56,700 --> 00:17:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] je puka taština.

387
00:17:59,599 --> 00:18:00,799
[SPEAKER_00] a dat krv na tašte,

388
00:18:00,799 --> 00:18:02,259
[SPEAKER_00] to znači na prazno.

389
00:18:02,259 --> 00:18:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ću ponoviti ono što sam vam rekao malo prije,

390
00:18:05,299 --> 00:18:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam otkrivao svoje zvanje,

391
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] da sve ono što sam želio,

392
00:18:08,900 --> 00:18:10,180
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi to dobio,

393
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] vidio sam da je moja želja veća od toga.

394
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] Jedini koji je bio kadar ispunit potpuno čežnju moga srca.

395
00:18:16,279 --> 00:18:18,259
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bilo neko stvorenje,

396
00:18:18,259 --> 00:18:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] nije bila neka okolnost,

397
00:18:20,119 --> 00:18:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] još manje ja sam sebi.

398
00:18:21,539 --> 00:18:24,259
[SPEAKER_00] Bio neko iznad svega toga.

399
00:18:24,259 --> 00:18:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] On ne samo da je ispunio moju želju,

400
00:18:26,059 --> 00:18:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] nego je nadišao.

401
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:28,160
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

402
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam rekao Bože u redu,

403
00:18:31,039 --> 00:18:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi tebe albio ovo.

404
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi tebe albio ovo.

405
00:18:34,099 --> 00:18:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] I osjećao sam podvojnost srca.

406
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:37,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da se lominu u sebi.

407
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:40,700
[SPEAKER_00] I tad sam upozao jednu frendicu u Palmotićevoj.

408
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je danas časna sestra.

409
00:18:42,579 --> 00:18:45,779
[SPEAKER_00] I šetao mi putem i ona meni kaže,

410
00:18:45,779 --> 00:18:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] znaš brate,

411
00:18:46,380 --> 00:18:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] sveci su ljudi koji žele Boga bez i.

412
00:18:49,579 --> 00:18:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] Bog i još nešto.

413
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,339
[SPEAKER_00] Bog i još nešto.

414
00:18:52,339 --> 00:18:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

415
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] On je moj sve.

416
00:18:54,539 --> 00:18:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] I želim se ono što dolazi od njega,

417
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:59,640
[SPEAKER_00] što će biti po njemu i za njega.

418
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:01,700
[SPEAKER_00] Toma veliki utemeljitelj Isovaca,

419
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] sveti Ignacio Loyola,

420
00:19:03,039 --> 00:19:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] govori o tantum kvantum.

421
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] Želim onako, kako, onoliko, koliko Bog želi za mene.

422
00:19:08,559 --> 00:19:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to je neusporedivo najbolje.

423
00:19:10,779 --> 00:19:13,319
[SPEAKER_00] I ako zaista volimo svoju budućnost,

424
00:19:13,319 --> 00:19:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] svoju vječnost,

425
00:19:14,579 --> 00:19:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] ljude oko sebe,

426
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] one kojima sam poslan,

427
00:19:17,599 --> 00:19:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] onda je suvudo išta tražit

428
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] mimo volje Božije.

429
00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ako hoćete, mimo volje Božije,

430
00:19:23,619 --> 00:19:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] križevi se množe.

431
00:19:24,559 --> 00:19:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] I oma što se dogodilo u Bosni i Hercegovini

432
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,700
[SPEAKER_00] prije domovinskog rata.

433
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dvije sestre, mlađe od vas,

434
00:19:30,059 --> 00:19:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] rani poberte, tamo tako reći.

435
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli su tati da im je dosadno kući,

436
00:19:36,539 --> 00:19:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] on je radio u staji sa životinjama

437
00:19:38,819 --> 00:19:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] i da bi otišli kroz šumu,

438
00:19:40,319 --> 00:19:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] čini mi se da to bio Mostar,

439
00:19:42,180 --> 00:19:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] neko obližnje mjesto blizu Mostara,

440
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] majka radila u Mostaru,

441
00:19:45,599 --> 00:19:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] ili nekom drugom gradu,

442
00:19:46,559 --> 00:19:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad je nevažno,

443
00:19:47,380 --> 00:19:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] da će oni kroz šumarak,

444
00:19:49,039 --> 00:19:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] tamo šumicu malo proći,

445
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] doći mami na posao,

446
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] da malo budu s njom,

447
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] jer je dosadno kući.

448
00:19:53,359 --> 00:19:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] Tati je rekao, nemojte,

449
00:19:55,359 --> 00:19:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] sprema se nevrijeme,

450
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] zna tata što govori,

451
00:19:57,619 --> 00:19:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] budite doma.

452
00:19:58,400 --> 00:20:00,359
[SPEAKER_00] Mama će doći poslije na kući,

453
00:20:00,359 --> 00:20:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćemo se družiti.

454
00:20:01,819 --> 00:20:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, njima možemo slobodno reći,

455
00:20:04,599 --> 00:20:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] vrag nije dam mira.

456
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što Adam u jevi,

457
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,220
[SPEAKER_00] nije vrag dam mira.

458
00:20:08,220 --> 00:20:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] I one su odlučili,

459
00:20:10,119 --> 00:20:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] ok je tata bio staj,

460
00:20:11,059 --> 00:20:11,740
[SPEAKER_00] šmugniti,

461
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:13,779
[SPEAKER_00] a, stićemo mi lako do matere,

462
00:20:13,779 --> 00:20:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćemo se s njome lipo vrati

463
00:20:15,099 --> 00:20:16,140
[SPEAKER_00] poslije otcu doma.

464
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] Došla večer,

465
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] vidili otac i mater,

466
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] dene i drugi večer i nema.

467
00:20:23,519 --> 00:20:26,740
[SPEAKER_00] A meća van je samo da se spremila,

468
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] ne vrijeme,

469
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:30,279
[SPEAKER_00] nego je ne vrijeme već par sati van.

470
00:20:30,279 --> 00:20:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] Otac je mislio,

471
00:20:32,099 --> 00:20:34,240
[SPEAKER_00] da su dica kod susjeda.

472
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:36,279
[SPEAKER_00] Isto je mislila i mater.

473
00:20:36,279 --> 00:20:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi nakraju,

474
00:20:38,460 --> 00:20:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] kad su odšli kod susjeda,

475
00:20:39,599 --> 00:20:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] shvateli da nema njihove djece tamo.

476
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] I počela tu noć potraga.

477
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Trajala je danima.

478
00:20:45,599 --> 00:20:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] I konačno su ih našli,

479
00:20:48,779 --> 00:20:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] skoro pred smrt.

480
00:20:50,819 --> 00:20:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] Samo što se nisu posve smrzli

481
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] od te mečave,

482
00:20:55,559 --> 00:20:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] pale su nez neki odron

483
00:20:57,619 --> 00:20:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] u nepažnji dok su išli prema majici.

484
00:20:59,619 --> 00:21:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pogubili su se.

485
00:21:00,579 --> 00:21:02,700
[SPEAKER_00] Uspeli su ih pronaći,

486
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] spasiti,

487
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] noge su im se smrzle

488
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] i morali su amputirati obe noge.

489
00:21:08,079 --> 00:21:11,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su došli novnari u bolnicu,

490
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] pitali su te dvije sestre,

491
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] oni su kroz suze odgovorile,

492
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] žao nam je što nismo poslušali Otca.

493
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] Tad sam sad sjetio koliko,

494
00:21:22,420 --> 00:21:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] a vjerujem da svi imamo to iskustvo,

495
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] zato idemo na ispovjede,

496
00:21:26,059 --> 00:21:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] kako su slatki plodovi poslušnosti

497
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:33,660
[SPEAKER_00] i kako su gorki plodovi neposlušnosti

498
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu u životu.

499
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] Malopri sam spomenio da jedini Bogo čovjek

500
00:21:37,119 --> 00:21:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] koji je pobjedio smrt sotonu i grijeh,

501
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Isus Hriste,

502
00:21:39,619 --> 00:21:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] jedini Bogo čovjek,

503
00:21:41,079 --> 00:21:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] jedini spasitelj svijeta,

504
00:21:42,279 --> 00:21:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] sva naša istinska nada,

505
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,259
[SPEAKER_00] radi njega smo tu.

506
00:21:45,259 --> 00:21:47,240
[SPEAKER_00] On je rekao svoj crkvi,

507
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] ko vas sluša,

508
00:21:48,519 --> 00:21:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne ne sluša.

509
00:21:49,859 --> 00:21:50,720
[SPEAKER_00] Mi svećenici,

510
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:52,200
[SPEAKER_00] naši biskupi,

511
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] papa,

512
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] vi draga braćo lajci,

513
00:21:54,420 --> 00:21:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] redovnici,

514
00:21:55,519 --> 00:21:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] bilo tko,

515
00:21:56,019 --> 00:21:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] svi smo grešni, ranjeni i slabi.

516
00:21:58,039 --> 00:22:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] I nismo mi pametniji nego vi,

517
00:22:00,619 --> 00:22:02,140
[SPEAKER_00] pa zato ste došli ovdje da čujete

518
00:22:02,140 --> 00:22:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] da neko vama prosipa pamet.

519
00:22:04,279 --> 00:22:06,680
[SPEAKER_00] ja vjerim da ima puno plemenitih srdaca ovdje,

520
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] puno pametnijih glava nego što sam ja.

521
00:22:09,359 --> 00:22:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svatko nas može nešto podijeli

522
00:22:11,119 --> 00:22:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] s drugim što smo od Boga primili po crkvi.

523
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jer svi smo mi crkva.

524
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:17,240
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva je crpka milosti.

525
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] Reko bi voljeni papa Franju

526
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,220
[SPEAKER_00] da je poljska bolnica.

527
00:22:20,220 --> 00:22:23,339
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ko iznutra osjećate strah od volje Božije,

528
00:22:23,339 --> 00:22:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ste grešni, ranjeni, slabi,

529
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:27,339
[SPEAKER_00] navezani na neke osobe, stvari,

530
00:22:27,339 --> 00:22:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] dođi, rasplaći se pred Bogom

531
00:22:29,779 --> 00:22:31,740
[SPEAKER_00] i moli ga da te oslobodi

532
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] od svake navezanosti

533
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] jer to ti je kao da podapinješ sam sebi nogu

534
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] na putu slobode i sreće.

535
00:22:38,079 --> 00:22:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ono što na evanđelje odavno govori,

536
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:42,339
[SPEAKER_00] to danas znanost potvrđuje

537
00:22:42,339 --> 00:22:44,160
[SPEAKER_00] da čovjek što je slobodniji,

538
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] sebedarniji, to je sretniji.

539
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:49,240
[SPEAKER_00] Čuli ste svi za svetog Ivana Pavla II.

540
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ja sam imao milost

541
00:22:51,119 --> 00:22:52,859
[SPEAKER_00] njega upoznat,

542
00:22:52,859 --> 00:22:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] upravo dok sam bio predsednik Franjovačke mladeži.

543
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] U svoje vrijeme,

544
00:22:56,579 --> 00:22:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] tamo u Italiji, u Rimu,

545
00:22:58,859 --> 00:23:00,839
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je to bila 99. godina,

546
00:23:00,839 --> 00:23:03,259
[SPEAKER_00] poslije opet 2003. godini kronice

547
00:23:03,259 --> 00:23:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] na Trsatu.

548
00:23:04,039 --> 00:23:07,680
[SPEAKER_00] Za njega se kaže da je rekao,

549
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,259
[SPEAKER_00] makar ja dok sam spremao doktorat,

550
00:23:09,259 --> 00:23:11,880
[SPEAKER_00] nikad nisam našao strogo takav citat,

551
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:14,339
[SPEAKER_00] ali sam vidio da se iz njegovih misli

552
00:23:14,339 --> 00:23:16,720
[SPEAKER_00] i tekako može izvući ovaj zaključak.

553
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] Kad vi mladi slušate o volji Božije,

554
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:21,160
[SPEAKER_00] onda najvrhatnije sebi postavite pitanje

555
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:23,160
[SPEAKER_00] ko je moje životno zvanje?

556
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nakon poziva na život,

557
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] najvažnije je sljedeće životni poziv.

558
00:23:29,140 --> 00:23:30,799
[SPEAKER_00] Obratno, koji je?

559
00:23:30,799 --> 00:23:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] Još sam ja stvarno za brak?

560
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] Još sam ja da budem posvećen u svijetu

561
00:23:35,279 --> 00:23:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] kao Ivan Merc?

562
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] Da li sam pozvan u redovnički,

563
00:23:37,859 --> 00:23:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] svećenički stalež?

564
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin, ja se malo bojim,

565
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali znam da je bolje da ti zavapim.

566
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:48,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ti me upotrijebi ili ću se ja zloupotrijebiti.

567
00:23:48,339 --> 00:23:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ti me upotrijebi ili ću se ja zloupotrijebiti.

568
00:23:51,039 --> 00:23:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Pavol II.

569
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje još se oženite?

570
00:23:53,819 --> 00:23:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] Njegov prijatelj također.

571
00:23:57,759 --> 00:24:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali su znali, opet ću reći tu misla o meni tako dragu,

572
00:24:01,380 --> 00:24:03,160
[SPEAKER_00] ništa bolje od Božje volje.

573
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] Predao je svoje srce gospinom srcu

574
00:24:06,079 --> 00:24:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] i molio je da se očeva volja jedino spasanost

575
00:24:09,460 --> 00:24:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] na najbolja proslavi njegovom životu.

576
00:24:11,140 --> 00:24:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] Izašao je iz jedne duge ispovijedi,

577
00:24:13,599 --> 00:24:15,759
[SPEAKER_00] odlučio je postati svećenik,

578
00:24:15,759 --> 00:24:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] makar se u njemu toliko toga rušilo,

579
00:24:18,059 --> 00:24:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali bio slobodan i sretniji nego da je krenio drugačijim putem.

580
00:24:23,079 --> 00:24:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] A njegov prijatelj otkrio da ga Bog treba u brak.

581
00:24:26,019 --> 00:24:28,740
[SPEAKER_00] I poslije je molio da mu stavi osobu na životni put,

582
00:24:28,740 --> 00:24:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] da mu miče djevojke, a providi buduću ženu.

583
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] To je najbolji način kad molite za budućeg braćnog druga.

584
00:24:35,099 --> 00:24:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, prvo da li me zoveš u brak?

585
00:24:37,039 --> 00:24:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ako jesi, miči mi cure ili dečka

586
00:24:40,059 --> 00:24:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] i providi mi budućeg ženo ili moža.

587
00:24:41,799 --> 00:24:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, dodeš u časno i nađeš časnog čovjeka.

588
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, jako je važno da mi u svoju životu

589
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] dopustimo da kroz Boga oblikujemo svoj život.

590
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Božja ljuba, Božja volja stvara svece, istinske sretnike.

591
00:24:55,940 --> 00:24:57,839
[SPEAKER_00] Što je svet Ivan Pao II. poručio?

592
00:24:57,839 --> 00:25:01,140
[SPEAKER_00] Brak je dobara.

593
00:25:01,140 --> 00:25:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] To je Boži izum ljubavi.

594
00:25:03,079 --> 00:25:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] Celibat je bolji.

595
00:25:07,319 --> 00:25:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] Oslonjena sveto Pavla, to je tvrdio u knjizi ljubav i odgovornost.

596
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

597
00:25:12,980 --> 00:25:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog sve srnijeg i sve stranijeg posvećenja Bogu i dušama.

598
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, najbolje je što Bog za nekoga želi.

599
00:25:23,259 --> 00:25:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je Pao rekao apostol, vrijedan povjerenja, apostol naroda,

600
00:25:28,859 --> 00:25:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tko se ženi, dobro čini.

601
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tko ne podilje na srce, ide za gospodnom, još bolje čini.

602
00:25:33,980 --> 00:25:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Čak je rekao, volio bi da si budate bez te tijelesne muke kao ja.

603
00:25:39,319 --> 00:25:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, bio je svijestno da svatko ima svoj dar od gospodina.

604
00:25:42,940 --> 00:25:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kako prepozna gdje me Bog zove?

605
00:25:45,140 --> 00:25:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tri su načina.

606
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo duh, psiha i tijelo.

607
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo je, makar to ma zvučilo, izlizano, otrcano, ne znam kako,

608
00:25:54,059 --> 00:25:57,839
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nije otrcano, izlizano, to je ključno.

609
00:25:57,839 --> 00:26:03,339
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže naš narod, dobro utro, kada ustaneš, dobro se pomoli.

610
00:26:03,339 --> 00:26:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kada ideš na more, dva put se pomoli.

611
00:26:06,539 --> 00:26:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ako odlučiš za životno zvanje, pogotovo ako ideš u brak,

612
00:26:09,420 --> 00:26:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] tri put se pomoli.

613
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kad osjetite čista srca, ste se pričestili.

614
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znate da je Božja volja neizmjeno najbolja.

615
00:26:18,579 --> 00:26:20,700
[SPEAKER_00] Da ona vidi sve posljedice tvojih postupaka.

616
00:26:20,700 --> 00:26:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] Da sve gleda iz perspektive vječnosti.

617
00:26:22,579 --> 00:26:23,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj život brzo leti.

618
00:26:23,660 --> 00:26:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] I nosiš duboki mir da si za brak.

619
00:26:27,039 --> 00:26:28,839
[SPEAKER_00] Da imaš svoju djecu.

620
00:26:28,839 --> 00:26:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti je to najdublja čežnja.

621
00:26:30,619 --> 00:26:34,160
[SPEAKER_00] To je jak znak, pogotovo ako traje,

622
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:37,240
[SPEAKER_00] da te Bog zove na taj životni staneš.

623
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:41,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, ako uz to što te narav uče,

624
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] ako si normalan čovjek ili muškarac prema braku,

625
00:26:43,619 --> 00:26:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam to osjećao.

626
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] Vidiš da te neko iznutra tiho provocira,

627
00:26:48,099 --> 00:26:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali nenametljivo.

628
00:26:48,940 --> 00:26:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] Juve, meni se narav opirala,

629
00:26:51,579 --> 00:26:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] ali duša radovala kad se razmišlja

630
00:26:53,359 --> 00:26:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] biti svečenik na oltaru, ispovijedati.

631
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] Sjeća se kako mi moj župnik rekao,

632
00:26:57,299 --> 00:26:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] Antone, imaš zaručnicu,

633
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] ti mogu biti dobar čovjek,

634
00:26:59,519 --> 00:27:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] vjer učitelj, muž,

635
00:27:00,380 --> 00:27:01,680
[SPEAKER_00] odi sbor crkveni.

636
00:27:01,680 --> 00:27:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, ne mogu odriješiti,

637
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu Krista dovesti na oltar.

638
00:27:05,319 --> 00:27:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam zašto,

639
00:27:06,259 --> 00:27:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] u meni neka dublja radost,

640
00:27:07,519 --> 00:27:08,259
[SPEAKER_00] šira radost,

641
00:27:08,259 --> 00:27:09,099
[SPEAKER_00] viša radost,

642
00:27:09,099 --> 00:27:10,339
[SPEAKER_00] kad razmišljam o tome.

643
00:27:10,339 --> 00:27:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Makar me vuče moja djevojka,

644
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] voli mi.

645
00:27:13,380 --> 00:27:14,660
[SPEAKER_00] I tad sam shvatio gospodine,

646
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] u mi u kršćanstvu,

647
00:27:15,819 --> 00:27:18,299
[SPEAKER_00] ne odričemo se ljubavi i sreće,

648
00:27:18,299 --> 00:27:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] nego zbog prave i veće ljubavi i sreće.

649
00:27:21,579 --> 00:27:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tu vam vidi za čisto hodanje.

650
00:27:23,500 --> 00:27:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ne odričete se u čistom hodanju ljubavi i sreće,

651
00:27:26,579 --> 00:27:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] nego zbog prave i veće ljubavi i sreće.

652
00:27:29,519 --> 00:27:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] Već sada,

653
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,799
[SPEAKER_00] znate kad sam hodu sa svojom zaručnicom,

654
00:27:32,799 --> 00:27:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam čuo rađite savjet od svečenika,

655
00:27:34,559 --> 00:27:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] je li smijem se ljubiti i što sam ne smijem ljubiti,

656
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] je li smijem dodiriti vama i ne smijem dodiriti tamo.

657
00:27:38,460 --> 00:27:39,220
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam zbunjen.

658
00:27:39,220 --> 00:27:42,259
[SPEAKER_00] Udan sam opet, spomenit ćemo Božju volju,

659
00:27:42,259 --> 00:27:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] kleknio pred raspelo

660
00:27:44,119 --> 00:27:46,180
[SPEAKER_00] i pita Bože, kako ti gledaš na to?

661
00:27:46,180 --> 00:27:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] Svečenici imaju neke svoje verzije,

662
00:27:48,819 --> 00:27:51,660
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi volio biti ni prestrog, ni prepopustivi.

663
00:27:51,660 --> 00:27:52,759
[SPEAKER_00] Što ti kažeš?

664
00:27:52,759 --> 00:27:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta mi je ta došla,

665
00:27:54,579 --> 00:27:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] koja je na nadahnuta misao?

666
00:27:55,779 --> 00:27:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Sine, sve što ne bi ti htio,

667
00:27:59,039 --> 00:28:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] da neka tvoja, neki tvoj prijatelj

668
00:28:02,039 --> 00:28:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] radi tvoje djevojci.

669
00:28:03,039 --> 00:28:04,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi smijem niti.

670
00:28:04,839 --> 00:28:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nije tvoja žena.

671
00:28:08,059 --> 00:28:10,019
[SPEAKER_00] I dođe mi slika, idem u trgovinu,

672
00:28:10,019 --> 00:28:11,660
[SPEAKER_00] ja ako volim tamnu čokoladu.

673
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne vidi teta, ne vidi nikog,

674
00:28:14,599 --> 00:28:16,359
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam, neću ja nju pojesti,

675
00:28:16,359 --> 00:28:18,160
[SPEAKER_00] sa ovi malo gricka je li iza, smijem.

676
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,680
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde, neće niko vidi.

677
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,200
[SPEAKER_00] Malo tamne čokolade,

678
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] da se bare na vonja je na maršeta.

679
00:28:22,519 --> 00:28:23,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne smijem.

680
00:28:23,779 --> 00:28:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kupi, kao bude tvoja,

681
00:28:25,599 --> 00:28:27,319
[SPEAKER_00] onda je nosi liži, gricka i pojeti.

682
00:28:27,319 --> 00:28:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Otvorile su mi se oči.

683
00:28:30,539 --> 00:28:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tad sam shvatio da patr vatru sa afrekinu pravo,

684
00:28:33,519 --> 00:28:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] a ja sam mišlio da sam malo ovako pretjero.

685
00:28:36,839 --> 00:28:38,319
[SPEAKER_00] Tad sam shvatio da sam ja pretjero.

686
00:28:38,319 --> 00:28:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je važno da pusti Bogu

687
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] da oblikuje naše misli,

688
00:28:42,059 --> 00:28:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] osjećaje, odnose.

689
00:28:42,859 --> 00:28:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] I znate što?

690
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga sam imao najljepši period svoje veselje.

691
00:28:47,579 --> 00:28:49,240
[SPEAKER_00] Čistoća je kakvoća ljubavi,

692
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] a blud je zabluda o ljubavi.

693
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ponavljan, čistoća je kakvoća ljubavi,

694
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] a blud je zabluda o ljubavi.

695
00:28:56,119 --> 00:28:58,240
[SPEAKER_00] Zato pusti Božju ljubav,

696
00:28:58,240 --> 00:28:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] da ona tebe voli.

697
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] Najdraže mi je kad mladi kaoš,

698
00:29:00,980 --> 00:29:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] Bavlji časno, mi se volimo pa vodimo ljubav.

699
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne ljubav, pa sa lancu pa šivot.

700
00:29:04,579 --> 00:29:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] Da pusti da ljubav vodi tebe.

701
00:29:07,700 --> 00:29:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da ćeš iznutra osjećati

702
00:29:09,079 --> 00:29:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] ako zapovjedi Božje krši,

703
00:29:13,279 --> 00:29:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] taj se iznutra skrši.

704
00:29:15,119 --> 00:29:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sto posto.

705
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:18,160
[SPEAKER_00] To je ko gravitacija.

706
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:20,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne paziš na čašu, padne puca.

707
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:24,140
[SPEAKER_00] Tako isto, ako ja sa nemorama, posrćem,

708
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] nije grijeh nešto lijepo, a zabranjeno.

709
00:29:26,660 --> 00:29:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] Nego nešto pogubno, a zapakirano u fino.

710
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ja volim aforizme, pa sa jednom sebi drugima napisa

711
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:36,279
[SPEAKER_00] grijeh očara, začara, parazočara i razara.

712
00:29:37,359 --> 00:29:38,779
[SPEAKER_00] Mami, omani, pa odalami.

713
00:29:38,779 --> 00:29:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je lijepo shvatiti da Bog

714
00:29:41,980 --> 00:29:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad je dao neku zapoj da ti želi sve najbolje.

715
00:29:44,500 --> 00:29:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] Čude sam mi ovaj psalam

716
00:29:46,099 --> 00:29:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] koji smo danas pjevali za vrijeme Svete mise.

717
00:29:48,099 --> 00:29:49,700
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je to psalam 1.

718
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:52,299
[SPEAKER_00] Uživati u zakonu Gospodnje.

719
00:29:52,299 --> 00:29:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nije Bog proti naše sreće.

720
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] To je džavolska izmišljotina.

721
00:29:55,619 --> 00:29:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je ne kradljivac,

722
00:29:59,099 --> 00:30:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] nego tvorac tvoje moje sreće.

723
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Božja volja je na um

724
00:30:04,599 --> 00:30:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] na koje ja mogu do te sreće doći.

725
00:30:06,599 --> 00:30:07,740
[SPEAKER_00] već na ome svijetu,

726
00:30:07,740 --> 00:30:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] a pogotovo kroz čitavu vječnost.

727
00:30:09,619 --> 00:30:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] Samo predragi moji mladi,

728
00:30:11,579 --> 00:30:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] malo manje mladi,

729
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:14,680
[SPEAKER_00] mi tako lako zaboravimo

730
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] da ovdje tek privremeno boravimo.

731
00:30:17,079 --> 00:30:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] Za nas ljude,

732
00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] sve sigurno da ćemo što?

733
00:30:19,380 --> 00:30:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo, umriti.

734
00:30:20,019 --> 00:30:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što je drugo sigurno?

735
00:30:22,079 --> 00:30:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znamo kada.

736
00:30:22,819 --> 00:30:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je sada vrijeme milosti.

737
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,259
[SPEAKER_00] Sada je vrijeme spasa.

738
00:30:27,259 --> 00:30:30,759
[SPEAKER_00] Vraćam se na pozivu.

739
00:30:30,759 --> 00:30:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo znači iznutra osjećaš mir,

740
00:30:33,059 --> 00:30:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] da si za brak.

741
00:30:33,819 --> 00:30:34,799
[SPEAKER_00] Neko još veći mir,

742
00:30:34,799 --> 00:30:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] čuti da je za duhovni poziv.

743
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si za brak,

744
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,799
[SPEAKER_00] kako zna koja osoba za tebe?

745
00:30:39,799 --> 00:30:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ista logika.

746
00:30:41,599 --> 00:30:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] Da li imam mir uz nju,

747
00:30:42,859 --> 00:30:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je to to?

748
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da li imam zajedničke ideale?

749
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:47,200
[SPEAKER_00] Lako je za sporedne stvari.

750
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:48,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ona voli košarku,

751
00:30:48,339 --> 00:30:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] ja nogomet.

752
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ona voli split,

753
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja zagreb.

754
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nego u pitanju bitnih stvari,

755
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] da li sam to umiram.

756
00:30:53,339 --> 00:30:54,700
[SPEAKER_00] I treće je,

757
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:56,740
[SPEAKER_00] da li postoji dostatna naklonost.

758
00:30:56,740 --> 00:30:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto žene sa nekog običnog prijatelja,

759
00:30:58,980 --> 00:30:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] prijateljica.

760
00:30:59,579 --> 00:31:02,220
[SPEAKER_00] Mora postoje neka privlačnost.

761
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tako isto po pitanju

762
00:31:04,039 --> 00:31:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] ostvarenja duhovnog azvanja.

763
00:31:05,599 --> 00:31:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] Nije dovoljno reći,

764
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] ja ženi posta svećenik.

765
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine, pokaže mi gdje.

766
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:12,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znate zašto vam to govori?

767
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Pavod drugi,

768
00:31:13,819 --> 00:31:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] mogo se oženiti.

769
00:31:14,900 --> 00:31:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo da bi sebi uskratio mnoge milosti,

770
00:31:19,359 --> 00:31:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] koliko bi ovaj svijet bio osiromašen

771
00:31:22,220 --> 00:31:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] za milosti, za dobra,

772
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] da je Ivan Pavod drugi,

773
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu rekao ne.

774
00:31:25,380 --> 00:31:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da je na majka Terezija,

775
00:31:27,519 --> 00:31:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu rekla ne.

776
00:31:28,279 --> 00:31:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] Da je na blažnji alozi Stepinac,

777
00:31:30,220 --> 00:31:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji je također bio zaručen,

778
00:31:31,420 --> 00:31:32,140
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu rekao ne.

779
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] Da je fra Stjepan Brčina,

780
00:31:34,279 --> 00:31:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu rekao ne.

781
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:37,740
[SPEAKER_00] Imate primjer danas u našoj crkvi.

782
00:31:37,740 --> 00:31:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] Damir Stojić, Stjepan i ja,

783
00:31:39,759 --> 00:31:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] imali smo djevojke.

784
00:31:41,119 --> 00:31:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Razmišljali ozbiljno o braku.

785
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:45,720
[SPEAKER_00] I nismo se odrekli ljubavi sreće,

786
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:48,319
[SPEAKER_00] nego zbog prave i veće ljubavi sreće.

787
00:31:48,319 --> 00:31:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] To ponavljam zato što na džavo,

788
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] mediji, svijeti, naša pala,

789
00:31:52,519 --> 00:31:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] narav spominju drugačije.

790
00:31:53,819 --> 00:31:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kad sad sjetim 98,

791
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:58,799
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi smo bili sretni da je bilo 50 framaša u crkvi.

792
00:31:59,359 --> 00:32:01,200
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte vi sa ovo četvrtkom čaviće.

793
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam mislila,

794
00:32:02,519 --> 00:32:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] će mene pomest trema,

795
00:32:03,380 --> 00:32:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] ću im dođu ovdje.

796
00:32:04,079 --> 00:32:07,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je jako važno

797
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:09,099
[SPEAKER_00] u vašem i mom životu,

798
00:32:09,099 --> 00:32:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] da zaista, ne parolom,

799
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] nego činom od jutra do sutra,

800
00:32:14,279 --> 00:32:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] stavljam Boga,

801
00:32:15,539 --> 00:32:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] da bude kralj mojih misli,

802
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] kralj mojih osjećaja,

803
00:32:19,059 --> 00:32:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] kralj mojih odluka.

804
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] I da to činim zaista s čistom nakamom.

805
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:25,359
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, ne zato što ću tek dobro

806
00:32:25,359 --> 00:32:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] nešto od tebe najbolje,

807
00:32:26,619 --> 00:32:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] nego zato što si ti vrijedan svake ljubavi.

808
00:32:29,859 --> 00:32:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si vrijedan potpuno povjerenja.

809
00:32:31,500 --> 00:32:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ne želim ti se uskratiti radi tebe.

810
00:32:33,819 --> 00:32:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, Franju Asiški,

811
00:32:38,079 --> 00:32:39,819
[SPEAKER_00] utemeljite naših Franjevaca,

812
00:32:39,819 --> 00:32:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] jedan od omiljenijih svetaca

813
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] u katoličkoj crkvi,

814
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] je znao često plakat.

815
00:32:45,359 --> 00:32:47,400
[SPEAKER_00] Čak imao dvije operacije očiju radi toga.

816
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] U ono vrijeme to je bilo jako teško.

817
00:32:49,019 --> 00:32:51,759
[SPEAKER_00] I pitali su ga, Franju, zašto plaćaš?

818
00:32:51,759 --> 00:32:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što ljubav nije ljubljena.

819
00:32:54,559 --> 00:32:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što ljudi misle ukratko

820
00:32:57,079 --> 00:32:58,259
[SPEAKER_00] da će ih usrćiti nešto

821
00:32:58,259 --> 00:33:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] izvan Boga i njegove volje.

822
00:33:00,460 --> 00:33:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoguće.

823
00:33:01,460 --> 00:33:03,180
[SPEAKER_00] To je nemoguća misija.

824
00:33:03,180 --> 00:33:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] Sizifo posao.

825
00:33:04,500 --> 00:33:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite,

826
00:33:07,940 --> 00:33:10,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Pavo II,

827
00:33:10,259 --> 00:33:11,779
[SPEAKER_00] na njega ću se osloniti prije,

828
00:33:11,779 --> 00:33:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] na njegov primjer,

829
00:33:12,599 --> 00:33:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] on je razmišljao da uđe

830
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] u karmeličanski red.

831
00:33:16,519 --> 00:33:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] zavolio je preko jednog lajka,

832
00:33:19,119 --> 00:33:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] posvećenog Jana Tiranovskog,

833
00:33:21,759 --> 00:33:24,240
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnost totus tus.

834
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] To je najbolji odgovor na volju Božiju.

835
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:27,839
[SPEAKER_00] Totalno sam tvoj.

836
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] sve moje je tvoje

837
00:33:29,900 --> 00:33:31,400
[SPEAKER_00] i sve tvoje je moje.

838
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] Biti slobodan od ega

839
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] i svega za Boga.

840
00:33:35,019 --> 00:33:37,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ušao tu duhovnost,

841
00:33:37,779 --> 00:33:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] totus tus,

842
00:33:38,579 --> 00:33:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji je šitavo

843
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] iz jedne prekrasne knjižice,

844
00:33:41,519 --> 00:33:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] rasprava o pravoj pobožnosti

845
00:33:44,460 --> 00:33:45,700
[SPEAKER_00] prema Blažnoj Djevici Marije,

846
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] koju vam svima preporučam.

847
00:33:47,259 --> 00:33:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] napisao je veliki mariologi svetac Montfort,

848
00:33:50,039 --> 00:33:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] Judevrgnjom Montfort,

849
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:55,339
[SPEAKER_00] jedan veliki francuski svetac i mistik,

850
00:33:55,339 --> 00:33:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] misionar pučki,

851
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] utemeljitelj morfotanaca.

852
00:33:58,380 --> 00:34:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] I on je od njega doživio

853
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:04,160
[SPEAKER_00] s tu knjižicu potica

854
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,160
[SPEAKER_00] da čita i dijela

855
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ivana od Križa,

856
00:34:06,380 --> 00:34:07,799
[SPEAKER_00] svete Tereze Avilske

857
00:34:07,799 --> 00:34:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] i zavolio tu karmeličansku duhovnost.

858
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, iznutra osjećao

859
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:14,199
[SPEAKER_00] da ga Bog zove u svećenički stalež

860
00:34:14,199 --> 00:34:16,800
[SPEAKER_00] i da bude diacezanski,

861
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] biskupski svećenički,

862
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] to samo vi što nosi obično kolar.

863
00:34:19,179 --> 00:34:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] Da imam pa ovo drugi posto karmeličani,

864
00:34:23,139 --> 00:34:24,860
[SPEAKER_00] pitanje je da li bi ikak postao papa.

865
00:34:24,860 --> 00:34:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] Majka Terezija čak ostkrila poziv u pozivu.

866
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je profesorica

867
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] u jednog drevnog reda

868
00:34:32,659 --> 00:34:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] u katoličkoj crkvi,

869
00:34:33,599 --> 00:34:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali je čula poziv u pozivu.

870
00:34:35,519 --> 00:34:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] Žedan sam.

871
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] I tad je počela pomaga

872
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] toj sirotinji u Kalkuti.

873
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko se očitovala Božija ljubav

874
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:44,780
[SPEAKER_00] u njeznom životu

875
00:34:44,780 --> 00:34:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] da ja kad sam čitao

876
00:34:46,500 --> 00:34:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] njezinu životnu priču,

877
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] taj njezin poziv budio

878
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] u meni poziv.

879
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom je došla

880
00:34:55,199 --> 00:34:56,719
[SPEAKER_00] na ulice Kalkute

881
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] i počela pomagati

882
00:34:58,300 --> 00:34:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] toj sirotinji

883
00:34:59,159 --> 00:35:02,219
[SPEAKER_00] i načelnik noj je rekao,

884
00:35:02,219 --> 00:35:05,780
[SPEAKER_00] sestro, ovo što vi pokušavate raditi,

885
00:35:05,780 --> 00:35:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] njih je na tisuće.

886
00:35:07,199 --> 00:35:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] Tko će to?

887
00:35:08,239 --> 00:35:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] A ona je samo postavila pitanje,

888
00:35:10,619 --> 00:35:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] kako se brojiti o tisuću?

889
00:35:11,980 --> 00:35:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan,

890
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] dva,

891
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] nasukala je rukave

892
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:16,360
[SPEAKER_00] i počela raditi.

893
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] Danas je njezne sestre širom svijeta.

894
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] vidite što znači Bogu govori trajno da.

895
00:35:21,239 --> 00:35:22,780
[SPEAKER_00] Da, Bože, da.

896
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] A grijehu i grešnim prigodama ne,

897
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] jer me zasljepljaju,

898
00:35:25,940 --> 00:35:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] zarobljavaju grijesi.

899
00:35:29,159 --> 00:35:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ići, traži tu grijehu sreće

900
00:35:30,639 --> 00:35:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] i kada tražiš u smeću.

901
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Još gore od toga.

902
00:35:33,420 --> 00:35:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] I novinar jedan kad je vidio

903
00:35:36,860 --> 00:35:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] što se s Majkom Terizijom događa

904
00:35:38,659 --> 00:35:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] na Kopusti godina

905
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] se to dijelo ljubavi širi

906
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] ko najveća zaraza pozitivna u svijetu,

907
00:35:43,739 --> 00:35:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] došao je pred jednog umirućeg gubavca

908
00:35:47,079 --> 00:35:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] i pitao ga je

909
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] kako je na ulicama Kalkute bilo

910
00:35:51,099 --> 00:35:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] a kako je sada.

911
00:35:51,900 --> 00:35:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] A onako

912
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] pola bez zubi

913
00:35:56,079 --> 00:35:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] pred smrt

914
00:35:57,260 --> 00:35:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] kaže gospod novinar

915
00:35:59,460 --> 00:36:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] na ulicama Kalkute

916
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli život sam živio kao štakor

917
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] a na rukama ove žene

918
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] kojim je nebo dalo

919
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] umiren kao anđeo.

920
00:36:08,739 --> 00:36:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite što znači

921
00:36:11,039 --> 00:36:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] poput svetog Franje

922
00:36:12,179 --> 00:36:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] majke Terizije Ivana Paola II. Zavapitu

923
00:36:14,460 --> 00:36:15,780
[SPEAKER_00] ta molitva se pripisuje

924
00:36:15,780 --> 00:36:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] svetom Franje

925
00:36:16,579 --> 00:36:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] njegovog je duha

926
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bože moj dopusti mi

927
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] da budem oruđe tvoga mira

928
00:36:20,699 --> 00:36:22,719
[SPEAKER_00] gdje mržnja da donosim ljubav

929
00:36:22,719 --> 00:36:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sumnja donosim vjeru

930
00:36:24,039 --> 00:36:25,639
[SPEAKER_00] gdje trama da donosim svjetlo

931
00:36:25,639 --> 00:36:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] svi bi oni mogli bit solidni

932
00:36:28,059 --> 00:36:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] muževi

933
00:36:28,679 --> 00:36:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] i očevi

934
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] i žene

935
00:36:30,619 --> 00:36:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] i majke

936
00:36:31,380 --> 00:36:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] i treba na sveti očeva i majke

937
00:36:33,579 --> 00:36:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali

938
00:36:34,079 --> 00:36:37,820
[SPEAKER_00] Božija volja je naše posvećenje

939
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] drugim riječima

940
00:36:38,980 --> 00:36:40,579
